OL,3,CDoctors strike ballot closes as third
OL,4,Cwalkout this year could be on the cards
OL,6,FA ballot of senior doctors in Wales
OL,7,Fover whether to strike, is to close on
OL,8,FMonday 4 March.
OL,10,FConsultants and specialists are
OL,11,Famongst those who have been balloted
OL,12,Fsince mid January by the BMA Cymru
OL,13,FWales union on whether to take
OL,14,Findustrial action.
OL,16,FThe move to ballot doctors came after
OL,17,Fthe union rejected the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment's first and final pay offer
OL,19,Fto members of a 5% increase for the
OL,20,F2023-24 financial year.
