OL,3,CDoctors strike ballot closes as third
OL,4,Cwalkout this year could be on the cards
OL,6,FAccording to the BMA, consultants and
OL,7,Fspecialist doctors have experienced a
OL,8,Fpay cut of nearly a third since 2008.
OL,10,FDr Stephen Kelly, chair of BMA Cymru
OL,11,FWales consultants committee, said "no
OL,12,Fdoctor wants to take industrial
OL,13,Faction" but "poor working conditions
OL,14,Fare driving senior doctors to retire
OL,15,Fearly, reduce their hours or leave NHS
OL,16,FWales."
OL,18,FTalking about the people they are
OL,19,Fcaring for, Dr Kelly added: "All the
OL,20,Fwhile patients get sicker, and
OL,21,Foutcomes get worse."
