OL,6,FHe said: "Investing in staff retention
OL,7,Fshould be the Welsh Government's
OL,8,Fnumber one priority when looking to
OL,9,Fimprove NHS services."
OL,11,FThousands of Welsh junior doctors
OL,12,Fstaged a 72-hour walkout last month -
OL,13,Ftheir second of 2024 - as they also
OL,14,Fcalled for better pay.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, junior doctors in England
OL,17,Fheld their own five day walkout from
OL,18,FSaturday 24 February. It is their
OL,19,Ftenth round of industrial action since
OL,20,FMarch 2023.
