OL,6,FThe future of General Practice (GPs)
OL,7,Fin Wales was questioned by GP leaders
OL,8,Fafter contract negotiations between
OL,9,FWelsh Government, NHS Wales and BMA
OL,10,FCymru failed to reach an agreement in
OL,11,FOctober.
OL,13,FAhead of the ballot closing at midday
OL,14,Fon Monday, a Welsh Government
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "It is
OL,16,Fdisappointing that the BMA are
OL,17,Fballoting their consultant and
OL,18,Fspecialist doctor members for
OL,19,Findustrial action.
