OL,6,F"We will continue to press the UK
OL,7,FGovernment to pass on the funding
OL,8,Fnecessary for full and fair pay rises
OL,9,Ffor public sector workers. Without
OL,10,Fthat additional funding, we are not in
OL,11,Fa position to currently offer any more.
OL,13,F"We remain committed to working in
OL,14,Fsocial partnership with the British
OL,15,FMedical Association and are available
OL,16,Ffor further talks at any stage."
